org.intellimate.izou.threadpool

Class TrackingExecutorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intellimate.izou.threadpool.TrackingExecutorService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executor, ExecutorService

    public class TrackingExecutorService
extends Object
implements ExecutorService
    This is a ExecutorService where the Source of every submitted Thread is easily identifiable.

    The future purpose of this class is to track which addOn started which task, which makes it possible to hotswap AddOns.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Leander Kurscheidt
